							<td valign=top align=left><span class=pn-normal>The community has pitched in and bought &quot;Gold Community Status&quot; for our EZboard again for another 3 months (it will expire on July 25, 2003). Thanks to everyone who pitched in!<br>
<br>
The mods have taken some precautions to curb spammers and &quot;jihad&quot; incidents that we've seen time and time again. These actions include adding &quot;Outwar&quot; and &quot;mysupersales&quot; and a few other key words to the language filter. It seems that Outwar and E-bay spammers are amongst the most frequent and most annoying so we've tried to concentrate on those. In regards to the &quot;jihad&quot; incidents (like with the Sullon Zek invaders) or anon spammers, we've put a 3 post per day cap on anyone who has less than 30 posts on the board already. Please note, actual Luclin community members who have less than 30 posts but want to get around this can contact a mod or post on the boards about it and any mod can assign you a title and new user level that will lift this restriction from you... so don't worry!<br>
<br>
- The Luclin EZboard Mod Team -<br>
(Aezaar, Vallorious, Meshugugget, Bishoopugget, and Bicrius)</span><br><span class=pn-sub></span></td>
